CHISE IDS
================================================================================

The IDS (Ideographic Description Sequence) data is derived from the
CHISE IDS package (https://www.chise.org/ids/), licensed under
GPL-2.0-or-later.

The development of the CHISE IDS package was supported by the
"Exploratory Software Project" of Information-technology Promotion
Agency (IPA), Japan. Some data in the IDS files are derived and expanded
from the CDP database developed by C.C. Hsieh and his team at Academia
Sinica in Taipei, Taiwan.

